Tawanda Manyimo bụ onye na-eme ihe nkiri na New Zealand a mụrụ na Zimbabwe.
A mụrụ Manyimo na Bulawayo ma ọ gụọ akwụkwọ na Tennyson Primary School, na Milton High School.

Manyimo hapụrụ ọrụ ya na nhazi na Zimbabwe n'afọ 2003, wee kwaga New Zealand mgbe ọ dị afọ iri abụọ na abụọ. Manyimo gụsịrị akwụkwọ na Toi Whakaari: New Zealand Drama School n'afọ 2011 na Bachelor of Performing Arts (Acting).
